Description: Analyse and visualise habitat connectivity in urban landscapes,
    accounting for barriers and buffer distances. Includes Shiny app for
    interactive analysis and report generation. Based on methods developed by 
    Kirk et al (2023) <doi:10.1016/j.mex.2022.101989>.
